snippet.title: FragPunk Gameplay Trailer - Closed Beta in Early October!
snippet.description:
Shard Cards🃏 can do anything! Prepare to combo and counter various card effects in the upcoming #FragPunk Beta Test this October! 

This is not your standard 5v5 tactical hero shooter so don't expect any two rounds to be the same. 

Apply now for the Closed Beta and get ready to bend the rules!

Steam: https://bit.ly/4cxfJib
Xbox: Apply through the Xbox insider hub.
We will give access when the test begins, and selected players will be notified immediately.
Wishlist on Epic Game Store: https://bit.ly/4durgQO

Learn more at: www.fragpunk.com 
Follow us on X: https://twitter.com/PlayFragPunk 
Join the Discord: http://discord.gg/fragpunk 
Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61560012848094 
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fragpunkglobal/
